            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My new opinion about this place,\nThis school has some advantages and some disadvantages.\n(I am a foreigner studying at this school.)\n\nAdvantages:\nCool environment with no sound pollution.\nSchool Canteen.\nPlayground (small)\nBig Field.\nCBSE Medium with NCC pursuit.\n\nDisadvantages:\nStrict and Aggressive Teachers (some)\nStudents use other languages in school.\nSwearing happens alot. (very common)\nSmart board is broken. (in every class)\nStealing HAPPENS ALOT TOO.\nThere are benches to sit on and no chairs (i find it difficult because i am a foreigner.)\nThere are writings on walls.\nThere is forced 2nd language. (somewhat okay).\n\nOkay done, i would personally give this school 3/10. This school could be so much better if fixed the disadvantages with more strict rules and not learning.\n(Smart learning should also be implemented)\nPeace.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
