            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It is just opposite Baguiati thana....10  to 15 mins from VIP Road,  Baguiati....the school has a more or less big  open space for childrentoplay. ...rules and regulations are strict for the children that I observed with in my half an hour visiting time....the children participate in extra curricular activities because some children were selected on state level, that was informed when I was waiting there....teachers are cooperative as per my observations.",
